history.proof: intros m x y. split. - intros H. unfold satisfies in H. destruct tpSM. pose proof (denote_andp x y) as H1. unfold Same_set in H1. destruct H1 as [H1 _]. apply H1 in H. apply H. - intros [H1 H2]. unfold satisfies. destruct tpSM. pose proof (denote_andp x y) as H. unfold Same_set in H. destruct H as [_ H]. apply H. split; auto.
